 {\n        assertThatThrownBy(() -> FactoryHelper.typeIndex(String.class))\n                .isInstanceOf(RuntimeException.class)\n                .hasMessageContaining(String.class.getName());\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777409497107}]}
